dct_title_s: Sketch map to illustrate route of expedition to Lhasa / by Edmund Candler.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Followed route  from Siliguri Ry Stn to Lhasa is shown in red, dates are noted. Book held in RECAP, under call number: DS785.C363 1905
